- Sequencing and album continuity: Both candidates present curated sequencing, but the consistent energy and uniform mastering of Candidate 2 better sustain a front‑to‑back immersive playthrough in the specific AOR/hard‑rock way I prefer. Candidate 1’s cohesion is a plus, yet the sonic sparsity undermines the kind of layered journey I look for in a CD that “lets the medium shine.”
